            <span>我要写书评</span>
        </a>
        <h2>
            社会政治理论的重构的书评 · · · · · ·
            <span class="pl">(<a href="reviews">全部 1 条</a>)</span>
        </h2>
    </header>


        


<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="1386851">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1386851/" class="title-link">写得好，译得也好</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1386851"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/ananym/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1133666-5.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/ananym/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">不惑之境</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2008-05-23"
      class="main-meta">2008-05-23 15:33:27</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1386851_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  内容涉及很多社会学的研究，视野很宽广，谈到上个世纪中期的一些重要人物，默顿、斯梅尔塞等等。对方法论的反思很清晰、很到位。  译者是台湾社会学理论学者，有研究，故而翻译得很准确、明白。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 3没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_1386851_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_1386851_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










